---
description: Guidance on handling drizzle migrations 
globs: 
alwaysApply: true
---
---
description: General project rules that applies to all file types. Should be most general
globs: **/*
---
- Use the drizzle-kit cli to generate migrations automatically
- If a migration requires custom SQL not supported by drizzle then generate a custom migration using drizzle-kit
- Never hand-write SQL migrations into the /migrations folder
- Since drizzle-kit doesn't support up and down migrations, when you make a mistake, drop the old migration when you can and regenerate a new one. Avoid creating a messy migration history.